trans-unit.source: Defines an attribute that specifies the scope where a <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider"></xref> object should be applied when a resource is located.
trans-unit.target: Definierar ett attribut som anger omfattningen där en <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider"> </xref> objekt som ska användas när en resurs har hittats.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider> class parses and generates code during compilation for a resource that has a specific file.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider>klassen Parsar och genererar kod under kompilering för en resurs som har en viss fil.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider>

trans-unit.source: The FolderLevelBuildProviderAppliesToAttribute attribute defines the location scope for which the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider> object will be called.
trans-unit.target: Attributet FolderLevelBuildProviderAppliesToAttribute definierar plats som den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider>objektet kommer att avbrytas.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider>

trans-unit.source: By setting the FolderLevelBuildProviderAppliesToAttribute attribute, you can limit a <xref:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider> object to certain [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/add/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] directories, such as App_Code.
trans-unit.target: Genom att ange attributet FolderLevelBuildProviderAppliesToAttribute kan du begränsa en <xref:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider>objekt till vissa [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/add/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] kataloger såsom App_Code.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider>

trans-unit.source: If you do not apply a FolderLevelBuildProviderAppliesToAttribute attribute to a <xref:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider> class, by default, the attribute targets all directories.
trans-unit.target: Om du inte använder ett FolderLevelBuildProviderAppliesToAttribute-attribut till en <xref:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider>klass, som standard attributet riktar sig mot alla kataloger.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.FolderLevelBuildProviderAppliesToAttribute"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.FolderLevelBuildProviderAppliesToAttribute"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: The target directory that a <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider"></xref> object applies to.
Gets or sets the target directory that a <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider"></xref> object applies to.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger målkatalogen som en <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider"> </xref> objektet gäller.

trans-unit.source: The directory that a <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider"></xref> object applies to.
